dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Diablo quadrangle, Contra Costa & Alameda Counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle DIABLO, CA 1953, DMA 1659 IV NE - Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1980." "First printing, June 2005." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
